{"tid":2317800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12月初北上港人倍增日均2400　港婦：港疫情政治不穩","createTime":"2020-12-09T00:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T11:56:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":26,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe1db80f321d559ce113ca799b5ca3b07484230","tid":2317800,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:22:03.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎第四波疫情持續嚴峻，上周七日中有四日新增個案超過100宗，之後開始出現大批市民北上內地，本月1日至7日從深圳灣口岸出境港人日均逾2,400人，當中最多一日有3,060 人。若以12月1日與11月30日相比，單日人次高出達兩倍，若以上月及本月1日比較，出境港人增5倍。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者昨日早上（8 日）在港鐵元朗站巴士總站視察，發現等候深圳灣口岸巴士的人數較早前增加，平均每小時約20多人輪候。有中年女士形容香港疫情及政治不穩令人憂心，疫情以來已四度出境北上照顧病母。<br />\n<br />\n其餘大部份人表示，雖內地疫情控制較本港理想，但沒打算北上避疫，只是因工作或家庭要返回內地；亦有內地人來港工作數年，疫情下失業，無法支找昂貴租金而決定「返鄉下」。<br />\n<br />\n本港疫情嚴峻，政府11月29日宣布，全港中小學將在12月2日起暫課（停止面授課堂）後，本月初從深圳灣口岸出境的香港居民人數大增。據了解，近日深圳的指定檢疫酒店爆滿，連帶珠海的指定酒店，也有不少香港人住，只餘日費百多元的平價酒店有房。<br />\n&quot;返去（北上）唔擔心，返嚟先擔心，上面啲人冇乜嘢，係香港好多（確診個案）搵唔到源頭。&quot;北上港人倪先生<br />\n<br />\n第四波疫情爆發以來，月29日首次單日新增個案「破百」，達到115宗。翻查入境處數字，上月30日經深圳灣口岸出境的香港居民只有914人，但到本月1日出境港人數增達兩倍，,至2,704人。<br />\n<br />\n若以12月1日與11月1日（444人）相比，經深圳灣出境港人增幅達5倍；而本月1日至5日再有三日「破百」，同期平均每日經深圳灣返內地的港人逾2,800人，當中本月2日就有3,060人；其後才開始回落，12月6日及7日經深圳灣出境港人分別為1,761人及1,354人。若以12月首七天計算，經深圳灣口岸出境港人平均每日逾2,400人。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者昨日早上（8日）在元朗巴士站視察近三小時，有近50人輪候前往深圳灣口岸的B2巴士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201208/412988466096246784697251.jpeg/embDbKn8xdmf7VLdNS6bmCKH67tQVvuA21zPH_Fczx8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201208%2F412988466096246784697251.jpeg%2FembDbKn8xdmf7VLdNS6bmCKH67tQVvuA21zPH_Fczx8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9c8131e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賴女士形容香港疫情嚴重，政治不穩，加上母親生病需人照顧，故即使北上要檢疫，過去一年來也四度北上，是次將視乎母親病情決定何時回港，「香港無大陸咁好，又暴亂又有疫情，大陸安全啲，喺香港住係會驚。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201208/412986437869244416169358.jpeg/89CwtURt-SzSInk0m_aVAGth366tlKTXMD3WPho91j4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201208%2F412986437869244416169358.jpeg%2F89CwtURt-SzSInk0m_aVAGth366tlKTXMD3WPho91j4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e49a2604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區先生：對香港醫療較安心 工作需要始北上<br />\n其餘大部份人反映北上是因工作或家庭需要，與香港爆發疫情關係不大。從事電子工程的區先生表示，即使深圳管控疫情略見成效，惟家人在港，且他對香港醫療較有信心，直言若非工作需要，不會考慮北上，「年初四開始無返過內地，但係真係做嘢都冇辦法......香港醫療安心啲，留係香港安全啲，有乜事都即刻有人接應你。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201208/412986706971594752670348.jpeg/NfBvmNX_JeuLeO1IJh8zbjeafN9AoebTu8rkp5LK5Kc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201208%2F412986706971594752670348.jpeg%2FNfBvmNX_JeuLeO1IJh8zbjeafN9AoebTu8rkp5LK5Kc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7792179a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倪先生：北上檢疫程序繁複 料不多人為避疫通關<br />\n而現年50歲、從事飲食業管理層的倪先生亦認為，內地疫情控制得較香港好，但北上檢疫程序繁複，若非工作需要，不打算北上避疫，「返去唔擔心，返嚟先擔心，上面啲人冇乜嘢，係香港好多（確診個案）搵唔到源頭。但返去你估好過癮咩，又要檢疫，又辛苦......住酒店唔知咩人同你一齊一間房。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201208/412987169821429760462391.jpeg/GcDoyBdY1d_DjQtLEKZgxW8EijwVutqc-TKI49MyiOM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201208%2F412987169821429760462391.jpeg%2FGcDoyBdY1d_DjQtLEKZgxW8EijwVutqc-TKI49MyiOM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=63f1ba2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港薪酬待遇較好 返內地為高考兒子打氣<br />\n拿着兩大袋零食及護膚品的蒙先生說，一家原住在廣東省，疫情前他留意到香港養豬業工作收入較高，故來港工作，原定每月可返家兩次，但疫情爆發後，兩地通關不便，至內地疫情受控，香港疫情卻轉趨嚴峻，他連月一直無離港，多留在工作的農場及宿舍，直至聽到明年3月要應考高考的兒子稱，考試文件仍未辦妥，他才請假回家協助及為兒子打氣，「隔離14天好煩，而家（香港）疫情咁犀利。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201208/412990154886615040037418.jpeg/uANK95JHZu0SxVkeY1Oif65LkjFrvCCH6r2at8C9mrc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201208%2F412990154886615040037418.jpeg%2FuANK95JHZu0SxVkeY1Oif65LkjFrvCCH6r2at8C9mrc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=25399579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港漂疫下失業捱貴租 決定返回內地<br />\n元朗港鐵站的B2巴士站，昨天早上9時至12時，每小時約有20多人等候，B2班次由以往同時段約15分鐘一班，大減至每小時一班。為親友送行的李小姐說，朋友由內地來港從事文職工作多年，但疫情下失業，一直找不到新工，加上香港租金昂貴、支出大，故決定「返鄉下」過年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201208/412988698905415680091326.jpeg/p2eJwGIOnIy1UmoozICNercj9boQg4psZ1bmbXJW5m0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201208%2F412988698905415680091326.jpeg%2Fp2eJwGIOnIy1UmoozICNercj9boQg4psZ1bmbXJW5m0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=66cc757d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b84ea942b77953a075333bd69020cdf283285ef","tid":2317800,"uid":209024,"like":165,"dislike":0,"score":165,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"支那人返支那，正常不過。"},{"pid":"e308c23612a98e8136513ae96df693b646c238ff","tid":2317800,"uid":33868,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"政治不穩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48228998888469c7898cc18456f3cbfd7ee7bfd","tid":2317800,"uid":61280,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"1b84ea942b77953a075333bd69020cdf283285ef","tid":2317800,"uid":209024,"like":165,"dislike":0,"score":165,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"支那人返支那，正常不過。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:33:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">港人？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n養豬，漂妓，蝗爸......</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5600201385e5c6802df688474dcbcd936288d019","tid":2317800,"uid":36901,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:33:44.000Z","msg":"嘩..up乜撚野政治不穩<br />\n全部都係漢奸黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91875f5eca0a479b8abc80464d37206b282876dd","tid":2317800,"uid":3302,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:35:07.000Z","msg":"好波 全部社會垃圾<br />\n要清清瘀血"},{"pid":"4bc7718cb639874f702e8c76ea7b28898305145a","tid":2317800,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"腥港人同小蝗蟲"},{"pid":"6a262e7f608c392acaae6c8f24f36a77618a8cda","tid":2317800,"uid":282359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"在座咁多位都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有呢啲人同你一樣話自己係香港人，俾你都想移民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4317e321ebccf1109d09d26e70fae26bc925568","tid":2317800,"uid":48059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"廢柴返大陸 係精神既"},{"pid":"22cf66a2dc70fd63bff4266b1f541b28edfe79dd","tid":2317800,"uid":35820,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:39:25.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸，你哋係英雄<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/YL-HO-190722-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FYL-HO-190722-26.jpg&h=20a65f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣危害國家安全，拉得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c5dd1f6a97e6e98a29742d47fd4ad1dd720acd","tid":2317800,"uid":224801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:40:53.000Z","msg":"大撚膽，無反對派都政治不穩"},{"pid":"5eea745d6b839efe094047827e6e8517039bc540","tid":2317800,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22cf66a2dc70fd63bff4266b1f541b28edfe79dd","tid":2317800,"uid":35820,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:39:25.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸，你哋係英雄<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/YL-HO-190722-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FYL-HO-190722-26.jpg&h=20a65f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣危害國家安全，