ass=\"hkgmoji\" />乜嘢港人<br />\n<br />\n住香港嘅大陸呀"},{"pid":"b2d27b4154e0aaf069fe0906d327e42df5b73db4","tid":2317800,"uid":154585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港薪酬待遇較好 返內地為高考兒子打氣<br />\n拿着兩大袋零食及護膚品的蒙先生說，一家原住在廣東省，疫情前<span class=\"red\">他留意到香港養豬業工作收入較高，故來港工作</span>，原定每月可返家兩次，但疫情爆發後，兩地通關不便，至內地疫情受控，香港疫情卻轉趨嚴峻，他連月一直無離港，多留在工作的農場及宿舍，直至聽到明年3月要應考高考的兒子稱，考試文件仍未辦妥，他才請假回家協助及為兒子打氣，「隔離14天好煩，而家（香港）疫情咁犀利。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑工？"},{"pid":"5f2a75b57fc1ebe55a8764447aed4b2506138828","tid":2317800,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:01:41.000Z","msg":"返左去就唔好返黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a48f7c6fd098cb1c8971b029c9214623ad28fa","tid":2317800,"uid":25409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"新移民蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627731d5ffd1efc8b439b09b6f67707c1653b591","tid":2317800,"uid":70301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:05:30.000Z","msg":"黐撚線，香港人政治不穩係去英國加拿大<br />\n<br />\n有咩人會政治不穩走返去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9e8cd794ea79905ecdb9247c2299433bf40940","tid":2317800,"uid":189243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"腥港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59544691f8f8ed655189422e6086af6d999e3d52","tid":2317800,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"627731d5ffd1efc8b439b09b6f67707c1653b591","tid":2317800,"uid":70301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:05:30.000Z","msg":"黐撚線，香港人政治不穩係去英國加拿大<br />\n<br />\n有咩人會政治不穩走返去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 